ustry the marina bay sands has three story towers with approximately  rooms and suites atop the hotel is the sands skypark a park that is set on top of the three towers the park has vegetation an observation deck several restaurants and a swimming pool that seems to flow over the building the resorts location right next to the city center allows it to serve as an entertainment site for the local population and also a destination for business travelers and mice meetings incentive convention exhibition events a year after marina bay sands opened tourism to singapore shot up  and the economy expanded by  las vegas sands continues to look for new expansion opportunities it is keeping an eye on countries such as japan korea vietnam taiwan and thailand in the us the company continues to expand its  resort in bethlehem pennsylvania which opened in  to compete with atlantic city for some of the new yorkarea market las vegas sands has also talked about the possibility of a florida resort in europe adelson and his management team were in discussions with governments in madrid and barcelona in september  las vegas sands corp announced madrid had been chosen as the destination for the gambling resort project dubbed eurovegas more precisely in february  it was reported the town of alcorcón in the outskirts of the spanish capital had been chosen as the site for the eurovegas project it was expected to take about ten years to build six casinos twelve hotels a convention center three golf courses shopping centers bars and restaurants however in december  the eurovegas project was officially canceled and it will not be established anywhere in europe in q  the company proposed a seat facility for the oakland raiders football team the total cost would be an estimated  billion and the stadium would be located near the las vegas strip and unlv it would be codeveloped with city of industry californiabased majestic realty co by estimation the stadium could be ready for nfl games by  the proposal would require  million from private investors and  million in public funding the main benefit from a stadium near the strip is the benefit to tourism in las vegas political contributionsedit according to the center for responsive politics las vegas sands was the  contributor to federal campaigns during the  election cycle donating  million  to republicans by comparison during that same period  adelson drug clinic contributed  million  to republicans and  goldman sachs donated  million  to republicans since  las vegas sands has contributed  million to federal campaigns and since  has spent  million on lobbying propertiesedit image property location date opened sands expo las vegas nevada  the venetian las vegas las vegas nevada may   sands macao macau peninsula macau china may   cotai arena cotai strip macau china april   the venetian macao cotai strip macau china august   the palazzo las vegas nevada december   the plaza macao cotai strip macau china august   sands casino resort bethlehem bethlehem pennsylvania may   marina bay sands marina bay singapore april   sands cotai central cotai strip macau china april   the parisian cotai strip macau china september   las vegas sands also owns the four seasons hotel macao conrad macao holiday inn macao sheraton macao and the st regis macao at cotai strip macau china past propertiesedit image property location date opened date closed notes sands hotel and casino las vegas nevada december   june   the original sands hotel in las vegas  demolished on november   ownership and stockedit ceo sheldon adelson and his family currentlywhen own approximately  of the companycitation needed in december  the company completed its initial public offering with the ticker lvs on the new york stock exchange at a price of  per share only  percent of las vegas sands was put on the market adelson maintained  percent ownership of the company while its management and directors owned the remaining  percent in october  the companys market 