 single transaction recorded incorrectly to other errors in the accounting records the company said it will vigorously defend itself against that type of uninformed and misleading reporting referencesedit  a b c las vegas sands lvs annual sec income statement filing via wikinvest  a b c las vegas sands lvs annual sec balance sheet filing via wikinvest  httpswwwstatistacomstatisticsleadingcasinocompaniesworldwidebyrevenue  a b c d stutz howard  december  investors las vegas sands hit jackpot as stock goes public las vegas reviewjournal archived from the original on  december    coffee with mike las vegas sands blog  april    puvaneswary s july   las vegas sands eyes south korea ir ttgmice retrieved  october    las vegas sands names madrid as preferred location for european development las vegas sands  september  archived from the original on  september    spains alcorcon town chosen for eurovegas resort  february    vegas sands picks madrid for eurovegas project cbsnewscom  september  dead link  tobias buck madrid  dec  sheldon adelson cancels bn eurovegas project in spain financial times london retrieved  dec    a b las vegas sands owner in talks for  billion stadium for raiders  costar group wwwcostarcom retrieved    a b top organization contributors opensecretsorg center for responsive politics retrieved  june    organizations las vegas sands opensecretsorg center for responsive politics retrieved  june    global airline guide  part two airliner world november    accessdate requires url help  httpwwwplanespottersnetairlinelasvegassandscorporation aircraft fleet details  schwirtz michael march   in filing casino operator admits likely violation of an antibribery law the new york times   a b archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved   external linksedit las vegas sands v t e las vegas sands corporation nevada palazzo venetian sands expo and convention center pennsylvania sands bethlehem macau cotai strip four seasons hotel macao sands cotai central sand