uct to enhance other digital products work with internal information technology resources and external partners to develop technology roadmaps and release processes and schedules assist in the development and deliver against the product roadmap as defined by the digital marketing and ecommerce leadership teams interpret overall marketing and ecommerce vision to create and implement the strategy and manage execution oversee product life cycle from strategic planning execution deployment and analysis work closely with digital marketing it and internal business units to capture business requirements and use cases to turn them into products that can be measured and optimized on a continual basis specify market requirements for current and future products through market research session data and competitive analysis supported by ongoing testing and optimization programs act as the project manager for all changes and enhancements to ensure that stakeholders are kept up to date on deliverables and timelines provide professional guidance and leadership to project teams to realize the strategic business vision and desired results deliver wireframes and product recommendations to development teams aimed at driving world class enhancements additional duties  responsibilities create and manage product roadmaps associated with owned product areas and other assigned projects interface with vendors and internal company resources to communicate business product needs and priorities from a property perspective manage booking engine content merchandising and related operations communicates with all areas of the company working with internal and external partners to identify and define technology needs based on product and marketing business requirements be responsible for the customer experience of the organizationproperty find opportunities for innovation on behalf of our customers design and implement new products and features related to these opportunities measure and analyze all aspects of the business identify and drive operational improvements and cost reductions familiarize yourself with the products components and its potential impact on the market as a whole practice discretion when discussing the production rollout and maintain confidentiality evaluate market competition and position the product so that it appeals to consumers prepare launch events to coincide with consumers’ buying patterns write a gotomarket summary and introduce it to the rest of the department identify and approach potential distributors        create mission statement for product launch and forecast performance in individual channels consistent and regular attendance is an essential function of this job performs other related duties as assigned additional duties  responsibilities   company standards of conduct all venetian  palazzo team members are expected to conduct and carry themselves in a professional manner at all times team members are required to observe the company’s standards work requirements and rules of conduct team members are expected to behave in a manner that supports a harmonious work environment to help us deliver unmatched service to our guests and customers additional duties  responsibilities minimum qualifications  years of age proof of authorizationeligibility to work in the united states bachelor’s degree or equivalent experience is essential  to  years product management experience required minimum of  years’ experience in online businessecommerce environment minimum of  years analytics experience in online businessecommerce environment experience with development and maintenance of content management systems experience with web analytics and reporting tools familiarity with modern web development demonstrated success defining and launching excellent products ability to communicate clearly and effectively in english both in spoken and written form must be able to obtain and maintain required licenses such as a valid nevada drivers license